             I handle the reservations at the studio on the lower level of a ho
use that belongs to a good friend of mine.  I really enjoy this part of town, a
nd it is great to be offering comfortable & homey lodging for people coming fro
m around the world to experience Austin.[] 
 []


Overfull \hbox (2963.735pt too wide) in paragraph at lines 322--322
