                                 We\TS1/lmtt/m/n/10 '\T1/lmtt/m/n/10 re a respo
nsible, easygoing couple who enjoy Austin\TS1/lmtt/m/n/10 '\T1/lmtt/m/n/10 s fr
iendly atmosphere, good food, and great music. We enjoy gardening, reading, tra
vel, and renovating our hundred-year-old home bit by bit.\n\nOur best times in 
