             I handle the reservations at the studio on the lower level of a ho
use that belongs to a good friend of mine.  I really enjoy this part of town, a
nd it is great to be offering comfortable & homey lodging for people coming fro
m around the world to experience Austin.[] 
 []


Overfull \hbox (2963.735pt too wide) in paragraph at lines 917--917
[]\T1/lmtt/m/n/10 ## 4                                                         
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                 We\TS1/lmtt/m/n/10 '\T1/lmtt/m/n/10 re a respo
nsible, easygoing couple who enjoy Austin\TS1/lmtt/m/n/10 '\T1/lmtt/m/n/10 s fr
iendly atmosphere, good food, and great music. We enjoy gardening, reading, tra
vel, and renovating our hundred-year-old home bit by bit.\n\nOur best times in 
Austin are on bikes--you can see a lot, get some sun, and get around downtown w
ithout the hassle of a car.[] 
